OL,3,CGive me five years to fix SNP mess,
OL,4,CSarwar urges voters
OL,6,FScottish Labour leader Anas Sarwar has
OL,7,Furged voters to give him "five years
OL,8,Fto fix the mess" he says was created
OL,9,Fby the SNP.
OL,11,FSpeaking ahead of their manifesto
OL,12,Flaunch on Monday, Mr Sarwar said his
OL,13,Fparty was running in the Scottish
OL,14,FParliament election to "get the basics
OL,15,Fright".
