OL,3,CGive me five years to fix SNP mess,
OL,4,CSarwar urges voters
OL,6,FThe party has already announced a raft
OL,7,Fof policies ahead of the Holyrood vote
OL,8,Fon May 7, with a focus on the NHS,
OL,9,Fincluding cutting waiting times for
OL,10,Ftreatment and ending the 8am rush for
OL,11,Fa GP appointment by renegotiating the
OL,12,Fdoctor contract.
OL,14,FLabour has also committed to scrapping
OL,15,Fand replacing the business rates
OL,16,Fsystem and building a rail link to
OL,17,FGlasgow Airport.
OL,19,FMr Sarwar said: "Scotland needs change
OL,20,Fafter 20 years of SNP government.
OL,26,@{D@QOU
