OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1776052540
OL,3,CGive me five years to fix SNP mess,
OL,4,CSarwar urges voters
OL,6,F"We have all seen the mess John
OL,7,FSwinney and the SNP have made over
OL,8,Fthose 20 years: waiting lists have
OL,9,Fsoared, patients are being left in
OL,10,Fpain, families are paying more and
OL,11,Fgetting less, and too many people feel
OL,12,Four country is stuck.
OL,14,F"You've given the SNP 20 years and
OL,15,FScotland has paid the price.
OL,17,F"Give me five years to fix the mess,
OL,18,Fsave our NHS and deliver the change
OL,19,FScotland needs.
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOUyD@AOU
