OL,3,CGive me five years to fix SNP mess,
OL,4,CSarwar urges voters
OL,6,F"I'm standing to get the basics right
OL,7,Fand build a better future for Scotland.
OL,9,F"My first priority as First Minister
OL,10,Fwill be to put our NHS first by
OL,11,Fcutting waiting times, ending the 8am
OL,12,Frush for a GP and bringing back the
OL,13,Ffamily doctor.
OL,15,F"But this manifesto is about more than
OL,16,Fthat, it is about transforming
OL,17,FScotland, making life more affordable,
OL,18,Fcreating jobs and opportunity,
OL,19,Fbuilding more homes, backing our
OL,20,Fschools, fixing our roads and ending
OL,21,Fgovernment waste.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@AOUwD@AOU
