OL,3,CGive me five years to fix SNP mess,
OL,4,CSarwar urges voters
OL,6,F"This election is a straight choice
OL,7,Fbetween more of the same with the SNP
OL,8,For change with Scottish Labour."
OL,10,FBut SNP depute leader Keith Brown
OL,11,Fpointed to the unpopularity of the
OL,12,FLabour-led UK Government, saying:
OL,13,F"People in Scotland will be thinking
OL,14,F'we've heard this all before'.
OL,16,F"Anas Sarwar stood with Keir Starmer
OL,17,Fand promised voters 'change' two years
OL,18,Fago but Brexit Britain is more broken
OL,19,Fthan ever.
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@`O]uD@AOUxD@AOU
