OL,3,CGive me five years to fix SNP mess,
OL,4,CSarwar urges voters
OL,6,F"Anas Sarwar told Scotland to trust
OL,7,FKeir Starmer, he told us the Labour
OL,8,FParty would bring energy bills down
OL,9,Fand he told us they would save
OL,10,FGrangemouth.
OL,12,F"Well, Starmer has been a disaster,
OL,13,Fenergy bills are up and Grangemouth
OL,14,Fhas closed. No one will believe a word
OL,15,FSarwar says now.
OL,17,F"We know what we get with the Labour
OL,18,FParty ` we already have one disastrous
OL,19,FLabour government, we don't need
OL,20,Fanother one."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUyD@AOU|D@MO]
