OL,3,CGive me five years to fix SNP mess,
OL,4,CSarwar urges voters
OL,6,FScottish Tory deputy leader Rachael
OL,7,FHamilton said Scottish voters "know
OL,8,Fthey can't trust Labour".
OL,10,F"Anas Sarwar and Scottish Labour
OL,11,Fcampaigned tirelessly to install this
OL,12,Fdud Prime Minister in Downing Street,
OL,13,Fand they need to own the consequences
OL,14,Fof his disastrous government," she
OL,15,Fsaid.
OL,17,F"The country is paying a heavy price
OL,18,Ffor taking a punt on Starmer, and Anas
OL,19,FSarwar's belated, self-serving attempt
OL,20,Fto disown him won't wash.
OL,26,@oD@_OUpD@XO]rD@AOUvD@^O]yD@AOU
