OL,3,CGive me five years to fix SNP mess,
OL,4,CSarwar urges voters
OL,6,F"Scotland desperately needs change
OL,7,Fafter 19 years of decline under the
OL,8,FSNP ` but Labour can't offer that
OL,9,Fchange because they're part of the
OL,10,Fsame failed, left-wing Holyrood
OL,11,Fconsensus."
OL,13,FScottish Green candidate and former co-
OL,14,Fleader Patrick Harvie said: "We know
OL,15,Fwhat Labour in power looks like.
