OL,3,CGive me five years to fix SNP mess,
OL,4,CSarwar urges voters
OL,6,F"We've had a Labour government in
OL,7,FWestminster and they have chosen to
OL,8,Fkeep cruel Tory policies, inflict a
OL,9,Fracist crackdown on refugees and
OL,10,Fmigrants and arm Israel's genocide
OL,11,Fagainst Palestinians.
OL,13,F"They have stumbled from crisis to
OL,14,Fscandal and back again, with a prime
OL,15,Fminister so disgraced that even Anas
OL,16,FSarwar has called for him to resign.
OL,18,F"If that's what Labour has done in
OL,19,FWestminster then why would we want to
OL,20,Flet them run Scotland?
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOUzD@AOU
