OL,3,CGive me five years to fix SNP mess,
OL,4,CSarwar urges voters
OL,6,F"It doesn't have to be like this. We
OL,7,Fcan lower bills for families while
OL,8,Fdelivering for our climate.
OL,10,F"It is what the Scottish Greens did
OL,11,Fwhen we introduced free bus travel for
OL,12,Fyoung people and when we scrapped peak
OL,13,Frail fares. With more MSPs, we can do
OL,14,Feven more."
OL,16,FWhile Scottish Lib Dem leader Alex
OL,17,FCole-Hamilton said: "Only Scottish
OL,18,FLiberal Democrats are offering change
OL,19,Fwith fairness at its heart.
