OL,3,CGive me five years to fix SNP mess,
OL,4,CSarwar urges voters
OL,6,F"We have set out plans to cut fuel
OL,7,Fduty, fix the crisis in social care
OL,8,Fand end the ferries fiasco for good.
OL,10,F"If voters back us in the 10
OL,11,Fconstituencies where we are neck and
OL,12,Fneck with the SNP and on the peach
OL,13,Fregional ballot across the country,
OL,14,Fthey will get hardworking local
OL,15,Fchampions committed to action on the
OL,16,Fthings that matter most like
OL,17,Fdelivering first-rate health care ` so
OL,18,Fyou can see your GP, dentist or mental
OL,19,Fhealth professional when you need them
OL,20,Fand helping you with the cost of
OL,21,Fliving."
